## Migration Path

### Option 1: Gradual (Recommended)
1. Update one page per day
2. Test thoroughly after each update
3. Total time: ~1 week
4. Benefit: Risk mitigation, incremental testing

### Option 2: Batch
1. Update all pages at once
2. Run comprehensive tests
3. Total time: 2-3 hours
4. Benefit: Faster completion, consistent approach

### Option 3: Selective
1. Update only pages that need it
2. Leave others unchanged
3. Total time: Varies
4. Benefit: Minimal disruption, focused improvements

